  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> {{ "today" | date: "%B %d, %Y" }}</p>

  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>Bambino Therapy ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how our mobile application, Bambino LetterBoard (the "App"), handles information when you use it.</p>

  <h2>Data Collection & Usage</h2>
  <p>The Bambino LetterBoard App is designed to function entirely offline. It uses your device's built-in Text-to-Speech capabilities to assist with communication.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> We do not collect, store, share, or transmit any personal information, usage data, crash logs, or analytics from your use of the App.</li>
    <li><strong>App Content:</strong> Any text typed or words spoken through the App are processed locally on your device and are not sent to any external servers.</li>
    <li><strong>Internet Access:</strong> The App does not require an active internet connection to operate, further ensuring your privacy.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>Our App is suitable for use by individuals of all ages, including children. Because the App does not collect any personal data or connect to the internet, it complies with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) automatically.</p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time if our practices change. Any updates will be reflected on this page.</p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the Bambino LetterBoard App, please contact us at: <strong><a href="mailto:hima@bambinotherapy.com">hima@bambinotherapy.com</a></strong></p>
